Environment Info:
- MicroController:  ESP8266 (ESP-01)
- OS:               Windows 10
- USB to Serial:    Silicon Labs CP2102 USB to UART Bridge

Preparation:
  - Download CP2102 Driver from silabs.com
  - Download and Install Putty
  - Download the Stable esp8266 firmware from http://micropython.org/download#esp8266
  - Download and install Ubuntu from App Store
  - Install Python if it is not already installed on the OS
    Note*: You may need to run the command below (in Power Shell as Admin) atfer installing Ubuntu:
    Enable-WindowsOptionalFeature -Online -FeatureName Microsoft-Windows-Subsystem-Linux
  - 
